<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:49:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>超越锂：钠离子电池如何改变世界</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beyond-lithium-how-sodiumion-batteries-could-change-the-world</link><description>锂离子电池是现代世界跳动的心脏。它为 80 亿部手机、数亿台笔记本电脑以及快速增长的电动汽车和储能库提供动力。但电池市场出现了新的竞争者。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/beyond-lithium-how-sodiumion-batteries-could-change-the-world.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beyond-lithium-how-sodiumion-batteries-could-change-the-world</guid></item><item><title>哪些基因使人们更容易患抑郁症和其他精神疾病？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/which-genes-make-people-more-susceptible-to-depression-and-other-psychiatric-disorders</link><description>巴塞罗那大学的一项研究发现了近 20 个基因，这些基因可能导致某些人更容易出现抑郁、焦虑以及易怒和神经质等特征。这些基因受 RBFOX1 基因调节，该基因充当与大脑功能的几个关键过程相关的遗传网络的中心枢纽。研究人员表示，不同疾病和特征之间的遗传重叠可能有助于解释为什么它们经常同时出现在同一个人身上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/which-genes-make-people-more-susceptible-to-depression-and-other-psychiatric-disorders.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/which-genes-make-people-more-susceptible-to-depression-and-other-psychiatric-disorders</guid></item><item><title>为什么插电式混合动力车的实际油耗往往更高</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/why-the-actual-fuel-consumption-of-plug-in-hybrids-is-often-higher</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/why-the-actual-fuel-consumption-of-plug-in-hybrids-is-often-higher</guid></item><item><title>分析AI背后的隐藏规则。然后用它们重写这篇文章</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/analysis-hidden-rules-behind-ai-then-use-them-to-rewrite-this-article</link><description>像 ChatGPT 这样的聊天机器人因其简单而强大：询问任何问题，您都会得到答案。但您得到的答案不仅仅取决于您输入的内容。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/analysis-hidden-rules-behind-ai-then-use-them-to-rewrite-this-article2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/analysis-hidden-rules-behind-ai-then-use-them-to-rewrite-this-article</guid></item><item><title>日本太空探测器掠过小行星以测试行星防御</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/japan-space-probe-skims-asteroid-in-test-for-planetary-defense</link><description>日本太空探测器周日飞越了一颗近地小行星，以测试有助于保护地球免受太空岩石侵害的技术。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/japan-space-probe-skims-asteroid-in-test-for-planetary-defense2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/japan-space-probe-skims-asteroid-in-test-for-planetary-defense</guid></item><item><title>我们生活在全息图中吗？ |吉姆·哈利利的生活指南</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/are-we-living-inside-a-hologram-jim-al-khalilis-guide-to-life</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/are-we-living-inside-a-hologram-jim-al-khalilis-guide-to-life</guid></item><item><title>国际研究小组表示，我们在错误的人生阶段考虑长寿</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/international-group-of-researchers-says-were-thinking-about-longevity-at-the-wrong-stage-of-life</link><description>长寿科学对于许多研究人员来说是一个重要的话题：我们如何才能&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/international-group-of-researchers-says-were-thinking-about-longevity-at-the-wrong-stage-of-life2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/international-group-of-researchers-says-were-thinking-about-longevity-at-the-wrong-stage-of-life</guid></item><item><title>意识可以是量子的吗？我们现在可能有了答案</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-consciousness-be-quantum-we-may-now-have-an-answer</link><description>数学分析表明，作为意识先决条件的代理概念本质上不可能是纯粹的量子&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-consciousness-be-quantum-we-may-now-have-an-answer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/can-consciousness-be-quantum-we-may-now-have-an-answer</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼支付哈瓦那综合症赔偿，重塑专注于“定向能源生物效应”的团队</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/pentagon-disburses-havana-syndrome-compensation-rebrands-team-focused-on-directed-energy-bioeffects</link><description>五角大楼周五宣布，国防部已向受所谓哈瓦那综合症影响的人员支付了数百万美元，并将一个关键的跨职能团队更名为定向能源生物效应 CFT，以调查相关问题。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pentagon-disburses-havana-syndrome-compensation-rebrands-team-focused-on-directed-energy-bioeffects.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 10:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/pentagon-disburses-havana-syndrome-compensation-rebrands-team-focused-on-directed-energy-bioeffects</guid></item><item><title>阿尔茨海默病免疫疗法向前迈进了一步：I期试验报告积极结果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/immune-therapy-for-alzheimers-takes-a-step-forward-phase-i-trial-reports-positive-results</link><description>世界各地的数十个研究小组正在努力阻止、治疗甚至预防阿尔茨海默病，这种病在症状出现之前在大脑中悄然发展了十多年。尽管近年来取得了重要进展，但研究人员仍在继续寻找能够更有效地改变阿尔茨海默氏症和其他形式痴呆症病程的疗法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/immune-therapy-for-alzheimers-takes-a-step-forward-phase-i-trial-reports-positive-results2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 10:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/immune-therapy-for-alzheimers-takes-a-step-forward-phase-i-trial-reports-positive-results</guid></item></channel></rss>